\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 The\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0  lady coloured deeply and covered over her injured wrist. "He is a hard man," she said, "and perhaps he hardly knows his own strength."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 There was a long silence, during which Holmes leaned his chin upon his hands and stared into the crackling fire.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "This i\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 
s a very deep business," he said at last. "There are a thousand details which I should desire to know before I decide upon our course of action. Yet we have not a moment to lose. If we were to come to Stoke Moran to-day, would it be possible for us to see
\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 over these rooms without the knowledge of your stepfather?"
