\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "And you may expect us early in the afternoon. I have myself some small business matters to attend to. Will you not wait and breakfa\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 st?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "No, I must go. My heart is lightened already since I have confided my trouble to you. I shall look forward to seeing you again this afternoon." She dropped her thick black veil over her face and glided from the room.
