\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "I cannot imagine."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "I see many objections to any such theory."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 "And so do I. It is precisely for that reason that we are going to Stoke Moran this day. I want to see whether the objections \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 
are fatal, or if they may be explained away. But what in the name of the devil!"
